features: 【Practical 2 in 1 Design】:Nested from a large and small rectangle coffee table.Due to the unique detachable design, it can be used as a coffee table in the living room,and the small coffee table can be used as a side table.So you can buy two products for the price of one product.

【Height Adjustable Design】:The rectangle small coffee table can be adjusted to 3 different heights by adjusting the knob.The height of the table top can be up to 24.3inch,which can stand alone as a small side table or even work on it.The The default height can be used in combination,and the nesting coffee table with a distinctive appearance can decorate your living room.When the 2 coffee tables are at the same height, the extra large countertop can meet all your daily storage needs.

【Ample Storage】:The 3-tier open shelves provides ample display and storage space. The height of the shelf in the middle of the rectangle coffee table is adjustable, you can adjust the height of the shelf according to the items placed. The side pockets provide extra storage space for magazines, tablets, remotes, and other miscellaneous items,so that your living room can be kept clean and orderly,as well as easy to access.

【Strong and Durable】:With high-quality particleboard and steel frame,it ensure the stability and durability of the coffee table, with a total weight capacity of 110 lbs.The adjustable feet at the bottom can protect the ground and reduce noise while adjusting the height. Hot Tips: Before installation, ensure the screws match the holes. To avoid cracking the top panel, gently press down the screws with a tool.

【Easy Assembly】: The package is equipped with detailed installation instructions and installation tools, so it is easy to put the nesting coffee table set together. Kindly noted: please do a favor to check whether all accessories are complete after receiving the product. If not, feel free to contact us in time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality not too hard to put together
reviews.reviewText: This took me about 45 minutes to put together. Could have taken me 30 but I didn't read the instructions very well 😜You get 2 tables that are adjustable in height which you can put together or separate. I love the shelves because I can store things on them instead of just having my stuff strewn about on the floor. They're pretty sturdy and I don't think getting condensation rings will be a problem. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I couldn't be happier with this table
reviews.reviewText: The table is heavy and solid and still easy to move. For me, it replaced a table that was a lot deeper, and I just didn't need or want the depth. I have been sliding the one side of it closer to the sofa when I play spider solitaire, which is once or twice a day, and there has been no loosening, for about 5 days now. The wood is good, perfectly smooth, thrilled with the greige color, light and airy feel. The wood is definitely not easy to scratch and so the table holds up to being used as a work surface for me. The adjustable side works really well, is easy to do. The different levels are so smart. I have a tray that has my little tools in it, box cutter, screwdriver, etc., which was always on top of the other table, just looked sloppy. Now it's down on the bottom on a roll-out tray, out of sight but still right there. So great. The pouch on the side, thick, nice quality, 5 different slots. It gets screwed on x4 so it does not flop around. Assembly was easy, just follow along with what they tell you to do. It took me just over an hour.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful versatile rustic table for a good price
reviews.reviewText: This table was just what I was looking for to use for music storage in our pool house. The metal and wood finish blend well with our rustic eclectic décor. The metal is heavy enough and the finish wasn’t marred. The wood has a high gloss finish on all sides – protection I wanted because our pool house is not always acclimated. All of the parts were labeled and corresponded to the included instructions which made for an easy assembly. Not sure why there are a few empty holes in the metal frame when you’re finished, but it’s just like the advertised photos. The smaller table has adjustable height options so that you can make it the same height as the longer table or higher for an attractive offset. I chose the higher and placed our turntable there. The weight limit for the longer table is 66 lbs and the smaller 22 lbs. The heaviest object I have is our vinyl album collection, but I’m sure its below the max. Overall this is a beautiful versatile rustic table for a good price.
